# OPS/_llm/95 — vector mode: matches → @llm.context items.
#
# The same EMIT shape the keyword path produces — the gateway can't
# tell retrieval strategies apart, which is the point: swap the memory
# backend, keep the contract. (select.js emits nothing in vector mode,
# so the two paths never double-append.)
WHEN @src == "llm" && @llm.phase == "request" && ._retrieval.mode == "vector"
  EXEC "op://map"
